snippet.title: Cross Country USA gameplay (PC Game, 1995)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Cross Country USA, Dos PC game produced by Didatech in 1995 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/cross-country-usa/7241/
It is an interesting game with trucks.You learn different things from life.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.
